name: Kasssh
product_description: Kasssh allows ecommerce retailers to grow their sales by accessing new consumers. These consumers are those that pay online using cash, which was previously impossible. By adding Kasssh as a checkout option, consumers can checkout and pay at one of 28,000 locations across the UK from petrol stations to supermarkets and newsagents. Kasssh is a sully automated solution and as soon as the customer pays we instantly settle the payment into the ecommerce sites existing payment infrastructure.

name: Popp AI
product_description: Popp is building AI agents that sits on top of a candidate database and handles candidate conversations like a human. The primary use cases today are application analysis and conversational screening (via WhatsApp, SMS or Web Chat), but the product will soon support semantic ATS search, candidate re-engagement, rejection handling and intuitive role matching, amongst others.

name: Revcat
product_description: RevCat is an innovative, AI-powered platform designed to revolutionize revenue growth strategies for small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) and startups. At its core, RevCat functions as a Virtual Chief Revenue Officer, utilizing advanced artificial intelligence and machine learning algorithms to analyze a company's specific objectives, challenges, market conditions, and industry benchmarks.

name: Conversity
product_description: Guided Sales and consumer insight - We enable brands to gain visibility and insight into consumer profiles and mindsets across direct and affiliate channels through real-time consumer interaction, data collection and analytics. We offer a SaaS guided sales solution.  In simplified terms we provide quizzes on websites, instore for for campaigns that ask consumers about their requirements and then make product recommendations. We see significant increases in conversion rate but, by making the questions about the consumer, we also capture valuable cohort behaviour.

name: Dtime
product_description:
At Dtime, we are deeply committed to the transformative power of data. Our vision is to not only collect and analyze information but to turn it into a driving force for societal and business advancements. We understand the challenges that come with uncovering and utilizing data effectively, which is why we've dedicated ourselves to developing innovative solutions that bridge these gaps.
At the forefront of our offerings is Dtechtive, our flagship AI-powered tool. Dtechtive is not just another search engine; it's a specialized solution designed to delve into the depths of the internet and other data sources to discover relevant datasets that others simply cannot. This powerful tool stands as a testament to our commitment to advancing data discoverability, enabling our clients to uncover valuable insights that were previously beyond reach.
Our services are tailored to meet a wide range of needs in the data discovery domain. From acquiring priority datasets that are critical for strategic decision-making to offering white labeling services that allow our clients to personalize and integrate our solutions into their existing systems seamlessly. Furthermore, our internal search capabilities ensure that our clients can efficiently navigate and utilize their own data repositories, enhancing operational efficiency and insight generation.
We believe in the power of conversation to spark innovation and inspire change. That's why we've created a dedicated platform for dialogue within the data community. Through our Conversations section, we aim to share knowledge, discuss emerging trends, and explore the limitless possibilities that data offers. This commitment to community engagement ensures we remain at the cutting edge of our field, constantly learning and evolving.
Our impact and dedication to the field of data discovery have not gone unnoticed. Our participation in prestigious initiatives like the CivTech Accelerator Programme highlights our role as pioneers in the industry. Additionally, the evolution of our Dtechtive solution through such platforms demonstrates our commitment to continuous improvement and innovation.
At Dtime, we're more than just a company; we're a collective of passionate individuals driven by the belief that data can change the world. Whether it's through our cutting-edge solutions, our community engagement, or our contributions to the industry, we are steadfast in our mission to harness data as a catalyst for positive change. Join us on this journey as we continue to push the boundaries of what's possible with data.

name: Trebel
product_description: Trebel is a groundbreaking music service that's redefining the way people access and enjoy music. Launched in late 2018, Trebel aims to address the music needs of a global audience by overcoming common barriers such as income levels, lack of credit card access, and expensive data connectivity. By acknowledging that most of the world's 6.5 billion smartphone users do not pay for their music, Trebel has identified a significant opportunity within the music industry to enhance the experience and monetization of music consumption for billions of users. What sets Trebel apart is its unique approach to music accessibility. Trebel offers a legal and licensed platform that allows users to download and play music without an internet connection. This offline capability is a game-changer for users in areas with limited or expensive internet access, enabling them to enjoy their favorite tunes anytime, anywhere. The service is sponsored by global advertisers and partnerships with international music and media companies, which eliminates the cost barrier for users and introduces a novel way to monetize music distribution. Trebel's team consists of industry experts, technologists, and visionary entrepreneurs, all working together to solve some of the music industry's most pressing challenges. Their collective passion for music and innovation is embodied in the app's user-friendly interface and its expansive library, offering an array of musical genres to suit all tastes. From the executive suite to the development team, each member brings their personal touch to the service, reflected in the unique playlists that users can explore and enjoy. With its user-centric model, Trebel is more than just a music service; it's a movement to democratize music for everyone, everywhere. Trebel invites everyone to experience music like never before â€“ unrestricted, personalized, and with the ultimate convenience. Download Trebel today and take control of your music experience in a way that resonates with your lifestyle and preferences.
